# Known-malicious file fingerprints. One JSON object per line.
# Schema (fields):
#   sha256       (required) — hex sha256
#   ssdeep       (optional) — ppdeep fuzzy hash
#   tlsh         (optional) — TLSH hash
#   campaign     (optional) — campaign label
#   label        (optional) — usually "malicious"
#   file_pattern (optional) — file name this hash typically appears at
#   description  (optional) — analyst notes
#   source       (optional) — provenance
#
# Baseline ships empty — operators seed their own via the private overlay
# or via `python -m pkgsentry.store.seed_intel` after publishing their
# overlay pack at PKGSENTRY_INTEL_PATH.
